<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Report it to the police, contact your consulate or embassy, and apply for a new passport with the necessary documents.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What methods can I use to keep my valuable documents safe?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Make copies of your documents, store them in a safe place, and create digital versions. Act immediately if they are lost.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-24T07:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:51:22Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'a-guide-to-passport-and-document-security-in-turkey' );
