<p>A virtual tour is an experience that allows participants to explore a specific place online in a virtual environment. Usually created using 360-degree imaging technology, virtual tours offer participants a realistic tour experience.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Advantages of Virtual Tours</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
