mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/a-guide-to-hamam-and-sauna-safety-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<h2 id="turkiyede-hamam-ve-sauna-kulturu-gelenekten-moderne" class="wp-block-heading">Hamam and Sauna Culture in Turkey: From Tradition to Modernity</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The hamam is a tradition that dates back to the Ottoman Empire. Used for both cleansing and social interaction, hamams are an important part of Turkey&#8217;s cultural heritage. Traditional hamams usually consist of hot, warm, and cold sections. Visitors can receive various massage and treatment services in these areas.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In recent years, modern spa and sauna culture has also become popular in Turkey. These establishments offer traditional hamam practices with a modern twist, appealing to both locals and foreign tourists. Modern saunas are often enhanced with various aromatherapy and massage services.</p>
<h2>Turkey&#8217;s Most Famous Historical Hamams</h2>
<div id="chat-history" class="chat-history-scroll-container">
<div id="ea8007d9f8cde3e8" class="conversation-container message-actions-hover-boundary ng-star-inserted">
<div class="response-container ng-tns-c253944506-40 response-container-with-gpi ng-star-inserted">
